name: Righthererightnow
body:
# Project 3: Right Here, Right Now

***
This is the Final Project for the class CS 424, Fall 2014 session. In this project we are going to play around with real time data for the Divvy bikes, 311 data (abandoned vehicles, streetlights, potholes), CTA bus data (Public Transportation), and much more.
***

Team Members:
Prateek Garg
Hardik Prajapati
Peter Bekos
Junior Luna

***
The Public Excel for weekly progress can be found here: [Public Excel File](http://1drv.ms/1tFXoay)
